==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: clustered
<hw>clustered</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>growing close
together but not in dense mats; -- of plants.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>occurring close together in bunches or
clusters.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bunched, bunchy.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>clustered together but not coherent.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> agglomerate, agglomerated, agglomerative,
aggregate.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clusteringly</ent>⟦br⟧
